<Author>Kenny-Lyle
<Content>Location not a drawback. Would recommend the hotel to anyone who is wanting decent enough standard of accommodation without having to pay city centre prices.As with the rest of Germany , public transport is peerless and having had some trepidation about arriving at Schonefeld and having to get across to other side of Berlin, I made the journey in under 1 hour. From the hotel to Zoo is under 20 minutes with one change and it lies on the U Bahn line a few stops short of Spandau which is a seperate town completely.All in all I would definitely stay here again. 
