<Author>unspecified
<Content>An Exceptional Hotel This hotel is excellent. I have stayed in this hotel several times and have always been happy to return. It's clean, the rooms are comfortable (don't underestimate the benefits of decent, black curtains that really stop you being woken up at sunrise - sadly lacking from most hotels).The breakfasts are good, and without exception, all the staff are wonderfully friendly and helpful.The location is well out of town, but is literally next door to a U-Bahn station, so that doesn't matter too much. Allow 20-30 mins to get into the centre, depending on where you're aiming for.I thoroughly recommend this hotel, primarily for business travel but I could also see it having some tourist potential. 
